    "multicolumn_aEDmcc": {
      "type": "multicolumn",
      "blocks": {
        "column_zd3zTh": {
          "type": "column",
          "settings": {
            "title": "Evelyn",
            "text": "<p>\"My posture seems to be steadily improving.  Noticing less of a feeling of things pulling downwards around my whole skull.\"</p>",
            "link_label": "",
            "link": "",
            "youtube_video_url": "",
            "isNewTab": false
          }
        },
        "column_WcY9Ua": {
          "type": "column",
          "settings": {
            "title": "Harvwin",
            "text": "<p>\"I noticed the other day the area where my neck meets my upper back is more flat .  I always had a bit of kyphosis and rounded soldiers and it seems to be correcting.\"</p>",
            "link_label": "",
            "link": "",
            "youtube_video_url": "",
            "isNewTab": false
          }
        },
        "column_RL3Jrp": {
          "type": "column",
          "settings": {
            "title": "Margarita",
            "text": "<p>\"Im a long time practitioner of various forms of yoga and have been using Reviv for one week now.  I liked it so much I added using Reviv to my yoga practice.\"</p>",
            "link_label": "",
            "link": "",
            "youtube_video_url": "",
            "isNewTab": false
          }
        },
        "column_wg7Qhd": {
          "type": "column",
          "settings": {
            "title": "Heather C.",
            "text": "<p>\"I have been using Reviv every night for about a month now.  My main issue was brain fog and pain/migraines caused by a bike accident.  Since wearing it, i have had a migraine or any of the localised pain.  How amazing is that?  Also my neurological function has improved.\"</p>",
            "link_label": "",
            "link": "",
            "youtube_video_url": "",
            "isNewTab": false
          }
        },
        "column_7zTXrW": {
          "type": "column",
          "settings": {
            "title": "Heather P.",
            "text": "<p>\"I am obsessed with wearing it.  My disposition relaxes, my thoughts focus and I enjoy being ME.  And i have been so surprised at how much my energy is present all day, in shockingly steady form.  Wow.  I'm still trying to wrap my head around all this.\"</p>",
            "link_label": "",
            "link": "",
            "youtube_video_url": "",
            "isNewTab": false
          }
        },
        "column_wQEbxc": {
          "type": "column",
          "settings": {
            "title": "MrNobody",
            "text": "<p>\"Ive been able to drop my CPAP pressure by 25% after a week of use.\"</p>",
            "link_label": "",
            "link": "",
            "youtube_video_url": "",
            "isNewTab": false
          }
        },
        "column_gGaUTD": {
          "type": "column",
          "settings": {
            "title": "Dallas",
            "text": "<p>\"At work ive been uncharacteristically positive to the point where i can see in customers and cowokrers faces that im making their day better.  And at home im just more positive and talkative.\"</p>",
            "link_label": "",
            "link": "",
            "youtube_video_url": "",
            "isNewTab": false
          }
        },
        "column_TpWpUy": {
          "type": "column",
          "settings": {
            "title": "Genevieve",
            "text": "<p>\"I am having so much less pain, for the first time since 2021.  I could cry!\"</p>",
            "link_label": "",
            "link": "",
            "youtube_video_url": "",
            "isNewTab": false
          }
        },
        "column_fB3iGU": {
          "type": "column",
          "settings": {
            "title": "Andrew G.",
            "text": "<p>\"The biggest improvement has been my energy and mood during the day has greatly imporved.  Its made it much easier to 'dad'.\"</p>",
            "link_label": "",
            "link": "",
            "youtube_video_url": "",
            "isNewTab": false
          }
        },
        "column_B9Hgc6": {
          "type": "column",
          "settings": {
            "title": "Jason",
            "text": "<p>“Four nights with the guard and i have felt significant fascial release in the back of tmy head and neck and my lower back and my hips.”</p>",
            "link_label": "",
            "link": "",
            "youtube_video_url": "",
            "isNewTab": false
          }
        },
        "column_PydAf3": {
          "type": "column",
          "settings": {
            "title": "Jay",
            "text": "<p>“I can honestly say that my flexibility has improved.  Maybe by 5-10%.”</p>",
            "link_label": "",
            "link": "",
            "youtube_video_url": "",
            "isNewTab": false
          }
        },
        "column_xkgLYN": {
          "type": "column",
          "settings": {
            "title": "Meryl",
            "text": "<p>“At 72 I was in tremendous pain and it sometimes brought tears to my eyes.  Now 14 days into Reviv i am walking at a fast pace.  I feel no pain in my hip.  I am standing taller and im able to get in and out of my car without pain.  In addition symmetry is returning to my face.  Also my vision was a bit foggy in the morning and now its getting clear.”</p>",
            "link_label": "",
            "link": "",
            "youtube_video_url": "",
            "isNewTab": false
          }
        },
        "column_qg7LRx": {
          "type": "column",
          "settings": {
            "title": "Jack P.",
            "text": "<p>“Im starting to notice how my back isnt hurting as much while working.  And when im talking with someone i am actually able to remember and finish the sentence.  My brain doesnt spaz and panic as it would before.”</p>",
            "link_label": "",
            "link": "",
            "youtube_video_url": "",
            "isNewTab": false
          }
        },
        "column_hnnfHY": {
          "type": "column",
          "settings": {
            "title": "Shelly",
            "text": "<p>“Ive noticed my neck sore/stiffnessis improving. I also notice im not as forgetful.”</p>",
            "link_label": "",
            "link": "",
            "youtube_video_url": "",
            "isNewTab": false
          }
        },
        "column_BcY84A": {
          "type": "column",
          "settings": {
            "title": "Eliot",
            "text": "<p>“Im loving the feel/effect of this right away. This is the stretch ive been trying to do for years!”</p>",
            "link_label": "",
            "link": "",
            "youtube_video_url": "",
            "isNewTab": false
          }
        },
        "column_x3W9db": {
          "type": "column",
          "settings": {
            "title": "Caleb",
            "text": "<p>I improved quite quickly. I think 80-85% brain fog is gone.  The mechanism i still don't really understand but it's definitely from Reviv.</p>",
            "link_label": "",
            "link": "",
            "youtube_video_url": "",
            "isNewTab": false
          }
        },
        "column_emgPm8": {
          "type": "column",
          "settings": {
            "title": "Andrew G.",
            "text": "<p>“Im able to sleep much deeper. Its kind of hard to overstate how significant this is.”</p>",
            "link_label": "",
            "link": "",
            "youtube_video_url": "",
            "isNewTab": false
          }
        },
        "column_QDa3Up": {
          "type": "column",
          "settings": {
            "title": "Mary M.",
            "text": "<p>“I'm no longer snoring. Great!”</p>",
            "link_label": "",
            "link": "",
            "youtube_video_url": "",
            "isNewTab": false
          }
        }
      },
